                <h1>New report shines light on GoTriangle&#039;s faults for failure of Durham light rail</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/91405809-d964-4463-bb71-f35046afc840.sized-1000x1000.png?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;The&#x20;proposed&#x20;light&#x20;rail&#x20;would&#x20;have&#x20;a&#x20;stop&amp;nbsp&#x3B;along&#x20;Lasalle&#x20;Street&#x20;and&amp;nbsp&#x3B;Erwin&#x20;Road&#x20;near&#x20;Duke&#x20;Hospital.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>The proposed light rail would have a stop&nbsp;along Lasalle Street and&nbsp;Erwin Road near Duke Hospital.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
